"title": "5793: arrogance",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5793",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Proud and unpleasant behaviour towards other people, based on a belief in one's own superiority or greater importance.</p>\n<h2>Arrogance characterises the wicked person</h2>\n<h3>As an attitude of the heart</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:21-Mark7:22\">MRK 7:21–7:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job35:12\">JOB 35:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:2-Ps10:11\">PSA 10:2–10:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:3-Ps73:12\">PSA 73:3–73:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps86:14\">PSA 86:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps94:3-Ps94:7\">PSA 94:3–94:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:15\">MAL 3:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:28-Rom1:31\">ROM 1:28–1:31</a></p>\n<h3>Arising from self-confidence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:9-Isa9:10\">ISA 9:9–9:10</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:29-Dan4:30\">DAN 4:29–4:30</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:7\">REV 18:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:9\">EXO 15:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs20:11\">1KI 20:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs14:10\">2KI 14:10</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr25:19\">2CH 25:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:15\">ISA 28:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:49\">EZK 16:49</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos12:8\">HOS 12:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:4-Hab2:5\">HAB 2:4–2:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:9\">LUK 18:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:9-Acts8:10\">ACT 8:9–8:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:10-2Pet2:12\">2PE 2:10–2:12</a></p>\n<h3>Issuing in words</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps17:10\">PSA 17:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:51\">PSA 119:51</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:5\">JAS 3:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:3\">1SA 2:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:18\">PSA 31:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:69\">PSA 119:69</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps123:4\">PSA 123:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:7\">PRO 17:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:24\">PRO 21:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer43:1-Jer43:2\">JER 43:1–43:2</a></p>\n<h2>Arrogance is essentially rebellion against God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:43\">DEU 1:43</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam15:23\">1SA 15:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:16-Neh9:17\">NEH 9:16–9:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:29\">NEH 9:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job36:8-Job36:9\">JOB 36:8–36:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps5:5\">PSA 5:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:85\">PSA 119:85</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos5:4-Hos5:5\">HOS 5:4–5:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos7:10\">HOS 7:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:1-Zeph3:4\">ZEP 3:1–3:4</a></p>\n<h2>Arrogance may even be found in the church</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:20\">2CO 12:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:18\">1CO 4:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:17\">1TI 6:17</a></p>\n<h2>The godly should reject arrogance</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:13\">PRO 8:13</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:23-Jer9:24\">JER 9:23–9:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer13:15\">JER 13:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:20\">ROM 11:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:28-1Cor1:31\">1CO 1:28–1:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:7\">1CO 4:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor13:4\">1CO 13:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:8-Eph2:9\">EPH 2:8–2:9</a></p>\n<h2>God punishes the arrogant</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:17-Isa2:18\">ISA 2:17–2:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod18:11\">EXO 18:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam15:23\">1SA 15:23</a> <em>The LORD rejects Saul as king</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:15-2Chr36:16\">2CH 36:15–36:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:10\">NEH 9:10</a> <em>the arrogance of Egypt punished</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps75:2-Ps75:4\">PSA 75:2–75:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:21\">PSA 119:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:78\">PSA 119:78</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:11\">ISA 2:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:15\">ISA 5:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa13:11\">ISA 13:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer48:29-Jer48:30\">JER 48:29–48:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:31-Jer50:32\">JER 50:31–50:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek7:8-Ezek7:10\">EZK 7:8–7:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:20\">DAN 5:20</a> <em>Nebuchadnezzar deposed</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech10:11\">ZEC 10:11</a></p>",
